templates.name: Returns nodes containing your hint in their name and connecting edges
templates.cypher:
match (n) where n.name contains $hint return n as nodes, null as edges
union all
match(n)-[r]->(m) where n.name contains $hint and m.name contains $hint
return null as nodes, r as edges

templates.name: Returns nodes with [Select category] and connecting edges
templates.cypher:
match(n) where $label in labels(n) return n as first, null as second
union all
match (n)-[r]->(m) where $label in labels(n) and $label in labels(m) return null as first, r as second

params.name: $label
params.cypher:
match (n) with distinct labels(n) as labels
unwind labels as label
with label as label
where not label contains "requent" and not label contains "elated" and not label contains "nverse" and not label contains "Attribute"
return distinct label order by label

templates.name: Returns the whole attribute association graph
templates.cypher:
match(n) return n as first, null as second
union all
match ()-[r]->() return null as first, r as second

sceneActions.name: Likely other attributes based on nodes
sceneActions.cypher:
match(n)-[r]->(m) where id(n) in $nodes and not id(m) in $nodes with m, sum(apoc.coll.max(r.conditional_prevalence)) as factor order by factor desc limit 5
match(n)-[r]-(m) where id(n) in $nodes return r,m
